# Videos around cars - Vehicle dataset

The videos were shot around cars in daylight from all sides. Each video is up to 100 seconds long. Cars are divided into 2 types: **with damage and without damage**. 
Dataset volume: **1200 videos**.

# 💴 For Commercial Usage: To discuss your requirements, learn about the price and buy the dataset, leave a request on **[TrainingData](https://trainingdata.pro/datasets/Vehicle?utm_source=kaggle&utm_medium=cpc&utm_campaign=videos-around-cars)** to buy the dataset

# Content

In the dataset 2 types of videos are presented:
- cars without damages
- cars with damages

All videos are made around cars from all angles:
